{"type":null,"faqId":10766,"title":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）  发送彩信","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入消息菜单，选择<b>新信息</b>，撰写新信息；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">输入收件人和编辑消息内容；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">按菜单键，再选择<b>添加主题</b>（添加主题后自动转换为彩信）；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击文本框左边</span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31916\" width=\"37\" height=\"29\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">按钮添加附件，可以加入图片、音频或视频（添加多媒体文件自动转成彩信）；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31917\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">编辑完成后，点击<b>发送</b>。</span> \n\t</p>\n<br />\n</span> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<br />\n\t</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1500","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397716920000,"seriesProductName":"H30-T10,H30-U10","visitedTimes":20,"isUs